{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7b97511cf2","title":"大字报——声声怨","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2a0aaec86d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"7b97511cf2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"222c241b8a","name":"成都工学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b2e60033e7","type":"title","text":"大字报——声声怨","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"756a17e9df","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"c58614118b","type":"subtitle","text":"(原著名笔锋，成都工学院学生)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"81db212db1","type":"paragraph","text":"愁云弥雾、难见青天，是非真假难辩。棒打谁？伤毁何人？内部与敌我并立，斗、绑，打不敢吭声。大学设监狱，民主、自由、平等何在？打你下十八层地狱，难以翻身！血肉筑成他的幸福，唯我等何生。一点冤魂到云霄，青天犹存，湘江水易阙，含垢忍辱不能生。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"e82639dd85","type":"paragraph","text":"上文注解：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"a5346990d2","type":"paragraph","text":"1．我院在肃反运动中，扣发全校师生员工信件，和亲友从千里赶来相会，不准会面。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"71ca318527","type":"paragraph","text":"2．肃反后认为“可疑”同学的家信和朋友来信，要经检查。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"0d37245d33","type":"paragraph","text":"3．肃反后被集中学习人员，任意捆、绑、吊打，连最根本的住、卧起居自由都没有。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"668422615a","type":"paragraph","text":"4．放出后不向同学交代，使得被集中学习的人，被党团员冷眼看待。认为是低人一等。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"3817ab049f","type":"paragraph","text":"5．肃反后在工人中整顿劳动纪律时，威胁和任意开除正直敢言的工人，而把党团员家属拉入学校。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"},{"id":"31c7578f7d","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《四川省右派言论选辑3》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月25日。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2"}],"page":{"id":"bb2274c589","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b97511cf2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}